Package: sleeperapi
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper Functions Around 'Sleeper' (Fantasy Sports) API
Version: 1.1.2
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Nick", family = "Bultman", role = c("aut",
        "cre", "cph"), email = "njbultman74@gmail.com"))
Description: For those wishing to interact with the 'Sleeper' (Fantasy
        Sports) API (<https://docs.sleeper.com/>) without looking too
        much into its documentation (found at
        <https://docs.sleeper.com/>), this package offers wrapper
        functions around the available API calls to make it easier.
